# MYCA Docs Living (All Agents)

## When MYCA code changes

- Invoke **myca-docs** agent or update relevant atomic doc
- Atomic and living docs: **NO date in filename** (myca-docs keeps them current)
- Atomic docs: single component, under 150 lines
- Large docs: overview only; link to atomic docs for detail
- Run `python scripts/build_docs_manifest.py` after doc changes

## Trigger

- "update MYCA docs", "@myca-docs", "MYCA documentation drift"
